com.solacesystems.common.util.expression

Class BooleanExpressionArgument

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.solacesystems.common.util.expression.BooleanExpressionArgument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExpressionArgument

    public class BooleanExpressionArgument
extends Object
implements ExpressionArgument
    Evaluates to TRUE or FALSE. This is typically used by another ExpressionArgument to push on the expression stack as the result of it being evaluated.
